TAKT Task File Format
=====================

This repository uses custom governance tasks under `.takt/tasks/`.

Required fields:
- id
- title
- status (todo|in_progress|in_review|blocked|done)
- task
- goal
- constraints
- acceptance
- routing (v5 canonical)
- warnings
- declarations
- handoffs
- notes
- updated_at

Routing fields:
- required_teams (non-empty list)
- capability_tags (list)

Declaration item fields:
- at (UTC timestamp, YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ)
- team
- role
- action
- what
- controlled_by (non-empty list)

Declaration policy:
- include an initial coordinator triage declaration
- keep declarations and handoffs aligned by phase
- include `rule:<rule_id>` and `skill:<skill_id>` evidence in controlled_by
